Articles.Content: I want to know what all of the new names of the parts are (RT-05 Flea)

From Scott's video, I could see the RT-05 Flea and the RT-10 Hammer.

From previous dev notes, we have the LV-909 Terrier, AFAIK.

And the ones we have already in 0.90: Rockomax Poodle, Rockomax Mainsail, Rockomax Skipper, and technically the BACC SRB.

I also found an album on the /r/KerbalSpaceProgram subreddit today:

> [Javascript is disabled. View full album](//imgur.com/a/AMsiO)

It appears that the LV-45 is called Swivel.
